## 🗺️ Development Roadmap

### Phase 1 — Foundation (Weeks 1–4)
- [ ] Project setup (Electron + React + SQLite)
- [ ] Auth system (login, roles, session)
- [ ] Institution registration wizard
- [ ] User management (Owner adds Workers, Workers add others)
- [ ] Basic class and student management

### Phase 2 — Core Operations (Weeks 5–8)
- [ ] Attendance module (Card Marker flow)
- [ ] Fee collection module (receipts, outstanding)
- [ ] Timetable editor (Teacher weekly updates)
- [ ] Exam scheduling and mark entry

### Phase 3 — Student Portal & Analytics (Weeks 9–12)
- [ ] Student login portal
- [ ] Progress dashboards (charts, trends)
- [ ] Notes/tutes upload and download
- [ ] Report card PDF generation

### Phase 4 — Polish & Distribution (Weeks 13–16)
- [ ] Notification system (in-app + email/SMS)
- [ ] Audit logs & security hardening
- [ ] Backup & restore
- [ ] Electron installer packaging (`.exe`)
- [ ] License key system
- [ ] Documentation & user manual

