## 📁 Suggested Project Structure

```
educore/
├── electron/                  # Electron main process
│   ├── main.js
│   ├── preload.js
│   └── ipc-handlers/          # IPC for DB operations
│
├── src/                       # React frontend
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── auth/              # Login, registration wizard
│   │   ├── owner/             # Owner dashboard & settings
│   │   ├── worker/            # Worker management panels
│   │   ├── teacher/           # Teacher dashboard, timetable, exams
│   │   ├── card-marker/       # Attendance & fee collection
│   │   └── student/           # Student portal
│   │
│   ├── components/            # Shared UI components
│   ├── hooks/                 # Custom React hooks
│   ├── store/                 # Global state (Zustand)
│   └── utils/                 # Helpers, formatters
│
├── db/
│   ├── schema.js              # Table definitions
│   ├── migrations/            # DB version migrations
│   └── seeds/                 # Demo data for testing
│
├── assets/                    # Icons, fonts, images
├── resources/                 # User-uploaded files (notes/tutes)
├── package.json
└── electron-builder.config.js # Installer config
```

