## ✅ Additional Features Worth Adding

| Feature | Value |
|---|---|
| **Dark / Light mode** | Better UX for different environments |
| **Multi-language support** | Reach non-English speaking markets |
| **Student photo capture** | Webcam integration for ID cards |
| **Printable ID cards** | Auto-generated with QR code |
| **QR-based attendance** | Students scan QR to mark attendance |
| **Parent portal** | Guardian tracks child's progress |
| **SMS/WhatsApp alerts** | Fee and exam reminders |
| **Offline-first** | Works without internet (Electron + SQLite is perfect) |
| **Cloud sync** | Optional backup to cloud for disaster recovery |
| **Mobile companion app** | React Native version for teachers/students |
| **AI insights** | Predict at-risk students based on attendance + marks |

